## Non-Negotiables

1. **Never fabricate citations** - All references must come from real, verified sources
2. **Never claim AI writing is human** - Transparency about AI assistance
3. **Never compromise user data** - Privacy and security are paramount
4. **Never lock users in** - Export and portability always available
5. **Never discriminate by discipline** - Equal quality across all fields

